{"tid":1543423,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9.5 太子港殤悼念會 烈士頭七前夕凝勢！","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:56:44.000Z","uid":167548,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"aef3e18c893a5cd8095da6750b46fd75af0c80f4","tid":1543423,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"[沉冤得雪] 8.31太子死亡事件 根據本貼將可逼使港共陷入絕境！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agotovU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agotovU</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n每晚8時至9時前往太子車站控制室外下跪，為左有可能被毀屍滅跡嘅手足FoundingFather鬼可以唔要尊嚴去求人。全程禁止禧笑，蘊釀情緒放聲咁哭，哭鬧前向傳媒表達如果因此輕生你就是遮蓋成件事嘅罪人。<br />\n<br />\n目的只有一個逼使知情者最後嘅良知。<br />\n但是我可以話你聽港共慢慢滅緊口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成場行動主要目的製造年輕人普羅大眾不再信任滿口慌言嘅政府同埋黑警。<br />\n<br />\n我地只接受當晚所有一分不減嘅cctv佐證，並且片中一定要有各報直播記者嘅存在去1核實並唔是造假片段。<br />\n<br />\n並且向外媒宣佈香港人懷疑太子站發生屠殺事件，並且不信任政府，要求交出cctv證明其清白。我要同大家講定呢幾晚一定要製造無比悽厲嘅畫面比外媒，令佢地幫我地出聲，但強調現階段是懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n事件繼續發酵三天，呢幾日暫停所有勇武，並且每晚不對警方進行任何衝突對恃。<br />\n<br />\n直至星期五最後通牒，交出所有cctv證明其清白，否則向外媒宣佈8.31太子站發生大屠殺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢招是以退為進，用哭聲或沉默或跪求港鐵職員交出cctv，發酵三日三夜博取世界同情，逼佢交出cctv，即使好彩炒左車世界一樣會見到香港平民不再信任政府警察，將有效加快人權法通過。但不幸真是發生屠殺，支共將會即是引爆。</span><br />\n<br />\n死線是6/8，否則單方面宣佈此事屬實，已點樣有效加持其可信性，每晚哭得有幾慘得幾慘，跪爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑義士 平平安安</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大鑊 我懷疑我逼到中共讓步個個人是我！太子CCTV懷疑影到圍毆事件！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541699</a><br />\n<br />\n[簡易懶人包] 真相浮現，831太子站極可能真係有人死，已非坊間流言既程度<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542384</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">［突發］美國疑似確認831太子站有人命傷亡 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542187</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmBokHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmBokHh.jpg&h=c674028e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見有心手足已經幫手宣傳<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em> 9.6烈士頭七晚會</em></strong></span>。<br />\n但是宣傳遠不及聽晚 警暴集會 (包埋不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。<br />\n所以行動提早凝勢！你地要明白香港人被羊群心理影響極深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果今晚聚到保守有2-300百人獻花, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">烈士頭七先唔會寂寞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主題：9.5 太子港殤悼念會 烈士頭七前夕凝勢！<br />\n時間：1900 太子花海對出<span style=\"color: red;\">行人路</span><br />\n必需品：白色鮮花！有錢買埋蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動詳情：願白色燈光照亮花海附近行人路, 叫烈士一路好走！夠人一齊唱香港抗爭歌《願榮光歸於香港》！<br />\n注意：狗屋開咪當佢放屁，我地是嚟悼念手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上熱門, 搵文宣巴打做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3300570649bcdfc79040dfbf5eff13e57f3e23","tid":1543423,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1389a7f86a28cf571315237ec6f1060e04053409","tid":1543423,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"950abdfe6b7cc7d338b21e4d94cbe5d87d183426","tid":1543423,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦, 我唔想到聽晚個個去晒警暴集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想烈士頭七無人去, 你忍心佢孤孤單單上路咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efacb0123ed38c98ab96e45fe4d0d9c580624742"